        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your patron's breath becomes blizzard of obscuring, scouring ice that follows your target. The target attempts a Fortitude save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target takes @Damage[1d6[cold]] damage, and the spell ends.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target takes @Damage[1d6[cold]] damage and @Damage[1d6[persistent,cold]] damage. The persistent damage automatically ends when the spell ends. It is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Concealed] to other creatures, and other creatures are concealed to it.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but both the cold damage and the persistent cold damage increase to 2d6.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The cold damage and persistent cold damage increase by 1 (2 on a critical failure).</p>"
